CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 23 reads: "Church League Action - New Light and Central, two of the weaker teams in Centre Avenue YMCA League, were rivals Saturday. New Light won the game, 32-20, as Central continues looking for its first victory of the season. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: New Light and Central church league basketball teams, one wearing #9, playing on court in the Centre Avenue YMCA gymnasium with audience on balcony
